title: AXL-DC - The Clean Up 2016
description:
AXL-DC - The Clean Up 2016

It seems to be a successful union of G n'R Frontman Axl and AC/DC old School Hard Rock So Here are the last of the tracks I have I look forward to the future offerings from this Supergroup and cant wait to see who else will be appearing in this new rejuvenated band of rockers. With all the history between the all the assortment of skilled musicians the opportunities are as huge as the history of the franchises that being said im done for now. Here is the
